- content_for :head do
  %title
    Radial tattoos
.banner
  %p.white.description
    All Designs downloadable here are property of radialtatoos.com. This is a collection of radially symetric tattoo designs suitable for different genders, age groups and most of them are specific for different body parts. We have few premium tatoos whith a better resolution available on purchase if you need. Contact us if you want to sell your tatoo designs online or if you need any designs on demand.

.catagory-tabs.col-12
  = link_to 'Free', root_path, class: "tab pull-left #{action_name == 'index' ? 'current-tab' : ''}"
  = link_to 'Premium', premium_tatoos_path, class: "tab pull-left #{action_name == 'premium' ? 'current-tab' : ''}"
  .clearfix
- @tatoos.each do |tatoo|
  .tatoo.pull-left.col-lg-3.col-sm-4.col-6
    .tatoo-inner
      - unless true
        .free-label
          = 'Free'
      = link_to tatoo_path(tatoo) do
        = image_tag(tatoo.image.url(:medium), alt: alt_text(tatoo))
.clearfix
.pagination-links-main
  = will_paginate(@tatoos, inner_window: 1, outer_window: 0)
.footer.col-12
  .contact-no.pull-right
    Contact us +91 9747515133
  .clearfix